GLKitMark
================================

A simple OpenGL benchmark for the Haiku OpenGL kit.

Originally based on [GLMark](http://sourceforge.net/projects/glmark/)

License
-------
Released under the GNU GPL v2 license

Required development libraries
------------------------------
* libsdl > 2.0
* libgl
* libglu

Compile with
------------
	make

Execute with
------------
	./glkitmark
